abstract: As Nasdaq OMX sought to reassure the public, analysts said that the lingering effects may be to the company’s other expanding business lines rather than to its trading.
snippet: As Nasdaq OMX sought to reassure the public, analysts said that the lingering effects may be to the company’s other expanding business lines rather than to its trading.
lead_paragraph: As the company that runs the Nasdaq sought to reassure the public after revealing a computer breach to one of its systems, analysts said that the lingering effects may be to the company’s other expanding business lines rather than to its trading.

headline.main: Breach Tied to Nasdaq May Have Wider Effect
headline.print_headline: Breach Tied To Nasdaq May Have Wider Effect
